statements: SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareComponents;
SELECT component_name, manufacturer FROM QuantumHardwareComponents;
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareComponents WHERE manufacturer = 'IBM';
SELECT component_name, serial_number FROM QuantumHardwareComponents ORDER BY component_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareComponents WHERE specification ->> 'weight' >= '100' ORDER BY component_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareComponents WHERE manufacturer = 'IBM';
SELECT component_name, manufacturer, specification FROM QuantumHardwareComponents ORDER BY component_name ASC;
SELECT component_id, manufacturer, serial_number FROM QuantumHardwareComponents WHERE serial_number IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareComponents WHERE manufacturer IN ('IBM', 'Google') ORDER BY manufacturer DESC;
SELECT component_name, specification->>'type' AS component_type FROM QuantumHardwareComponents WHERE manufacturer = 'Google';
SELECT * FROM components WHERE component_type = 'Processor';
SELECT component_name, manufacturer FROM components ORDER BY component_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM components WHERE manufacturer = 'Intel' OR manufacturer = 'AMD';
SELECT component_name, manufacturer, component_type FROM components WHERE manufacturer = 'Nvidia';
SELECT component_id, component_name, manufacturer, component_type FROM components WHERE component_type = 'RAM' ORDER BY component_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM components WHERE manufacturer='ABC Corporation' AND component_type='Processor';
SELECT component_id, component_name FROM components ORDER BY component_name DESC;
SELECT component_name, manufacturer, component_type, COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM components GROUP BY manufacturer, component_type;

SELECT c.component_id, c.component_name, s.simulation_name, s.simulation_date FROM simulations s JOIN components c ON s.component_id = c.component_id WHERE s.duration_hours > 10 ORDER BY s.simulation_date ASC;
SELECT component_name, manufacturer, component_type, specification FROM components WHERE component_type='Memory' ORDER BY component_name LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_computers;
SELECT computer_name, qubit_count FROM quantum_computers WHERE manufacturer = 'IBM';
SELECT * FROM quantum_gates ORDER BY error_rate DESC;
SELECT simulation_name, simulation_date, simulation_results FROM quantum_simulations WHERE simulation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT computer_id, computer_name FROM quantum_computers WHERE qubit_count >= 50;
SELECT * FROM quantum_computers WHERE qubit_count > 50 ORDER BY computer_name DESC;
SELECT computer_name, manufacturer FROM quantum_computers WHERE manufacturer = 'IBM' AND qubit_count < 100;
SELECT * FROM quantum_computers WHERE manufacturer = 'Google' AND qubit_count BETWEEN 50 AND 100;
SELECT gate_id, gate_name, gate_type FROM quantum_gates WHERE error_rate < 0.01 ORDER BY gate_name;
SELECT simulation_id, simulation_name, simulation_date FROM quantum_simulations WHERE simulation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware_components;
SELECT component_name, manufacturer FROM quantum_hardware_components WHERE year_of_manufacture > 2010;
SELECT component_name, description FROM quantum_hardware_components ORDER BY component_name DESC;
SELECT spec_name, spec_value FROM component_specifications WHERE component_id = 3;
SELECT simulation_type, simulation_result FROM simulations WHERE simulation_type LIKE '%error%';
SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware_components WHERE year_of_manufacture > 2010
SELECT component_name, manufacturer, description FROM quantum_hardware_components WHERE manufacturer = 'IBM'
SELECT shc.component_name, cs.spec_name, cs.spec_value FROM quantum_hardware_components shc JOIN component_specifications cs ON shc.component_id = cs.component_id
SELECT sim.simulation_type, sim.simulation_result, logs.log_timestamp FROM simulations sim JOIN simulation_logs logs ON sim.simulation_id = logs.simulation_id

SELECT shc.component_name, cs.spec_name, logs.log_message FROM quantum_hardware_components shc JOIN component_specifications cs ON shc.component_id = cs.component_id JOIN simulations sim ON cs.spec_id = sim.spec_id JOIN simulation_logs logs ON sim.simulation_id = logs.simulation_id
SELECT * FROM qubits;
SELECT qubit_name, qubit_type, qubit_description FROM qubits WHERE qubit_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM gates ORDER BY gate_type DESC;
SELECT gate_name, gate_type FROM gates WHERE gate_id = 3;
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM devices WHERE device_type = 'Quantum';
SELECT * FROM qubits ORDER BY qubit_name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT qubit_id, qubit_description FROM qubits WHERE qubit_type = 'superposition';
SELECT gate_name, gate_type, gate_matrix FROM gates WHERE gate_type = 'Hadamard';
SELECT * FROM circuits WHERE circuit_description LIKE '%quantum%' ORDER BY circuit_id ASC;
SELECT device_name, device_properties FROM devices WHERE device_type = 'quantum-computer' AND JSON_LENGTH(device_properties) > 2;
